OL,3,CFormer leader of Reform UK in Wales to
OL,4,Cdeny alleged Russian bribery charges
OL,6,FThe former leader of Reform UK in
OL,7,FWales has indicated he will deny
OL,8,Fallegations he took bribes to make
OL,9,Ffavourable statements about Russia in
OL,10,Fthe European Parliament.
OL,12,FNathan Gill, 51, is charged with eight
OL,13,Fcounts of bribery and one count of
OL,14,Fconspiracy to commit bribery.
