OL,3,CFormer leader of Reform UK in Wales to
OL,4,Cdeny alleged Russian bribery charges
OL,6,FOn Friday, Gill, of Anglesey, north
OL,7,FWales, appeared for a preliminary
OL,8,Fhearing at the Old Bailey before Mrs
OL,9,FJustice Cheema-Grubb.
OL,11,FThe defendant's lawyer Clare Ashcroft
OL,12,Findicated he would deny the charges
OL,13,Fagainst him but asked that he not be
OL,14,Fasked to formally enter pleas yet.
OL,16,FProsecutor Mark Heywood KC told the
OL,17,Fcourt the charges related to the
OL,18,Fdefendant's time as a member of the
OL,19,FEuropean Parliament.
