OL,3,CFormer leader of Reform UK in Wales to
OL,4,Cdeny alleged Russian bribery charges
OL,6,FHe said that charges had been
OL,7,Fauthorised against the defendant's
OL,8,Falleged co-conspirator Voloshyn, who
OL,9,Fis believed to be out of the
OL,10,Fjurisdiction.
OL,12,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb set a plea
OL,13,Fhearing for 18 July and a provisional
OL,14,Ftrial before a High Court judge from
OL,15,F29 June, 2026 at the Old Bailey.
OL,17,FThe defendant stood in the dock
OL,18,Fwearing a blue striped tie and grey
OL,19,Fsuit, and spoke only to confirm his
OL,20,Fidentity during the hearing.
