OL,6,FThe conspiracy to commit bribery
OL,7,Fcharge alleges Gill conspired with
OL,8,FVoloshyn and "others" between 1
OL,9,FJanuary, 2018 and 1 February, 2020,
OL,10,Fand that he accepted "quantities of
OL,11,Fmoney in cash" which was "improper
OL,12,Fperformance by him of his function or
OL,13,Factivity as the holder" of a position
OL,14,Fin the European Parliament.
OL,16,FThe other bribery offences are alleged
OL,17,Fto have taken place between 6
OL,18,FDecember, 2018 and 18 July, 2019.
