OL,3,CFormer leader of Reform UK in Wales to
OL,4,Cdeny alleged Russian bribery charges
OL,6,FGill was stopped at Manchester Airport
OL,7,Fon 13 September 2021 under the Counter
OL,8,FTerrorism and Border Security Act
OL,9,F2019, the court also heard.
OL,11,FHe was first elected as a Ukip member
OL,12,Fof the European Parliament in 2014 and
OL,13,Fhis role ended when the UK left the EU
OL,14,Fin 2020 ` at which point he was an MEP
OL,15,Ffor the Brexit Party.
OL,17,FThe defendant led Reform UK's 2021
OL,18,FWelsh Parliament election campaign but
OL,19,Fis no longer a member of the party.
